reviewText: This review is of the sellars (MEASORCALL) misleading information.  The disc is a poor copy from apparently a VHS tape on a -R DVD.  While it's a very difficult film to get, I suspect if you can get a VHS studio released tape, you are far, better off.  Unfortunately the seller (MEASORCALL) says it's a 'Used like New' DVD.  That's like saying the car is used with minor damage when describing a junk-yard 'CASH-FOR-CLUNKER' with a siezed engine.  Buyer beware!
